or-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%A1t-T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-154g2r0JoH49oHn26Ggtig">Phát Tần Châu - 發秦州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nh%E1%BA%ADn/Quan-san-h%C3%A0nh/poem-X59bjDm9u62zkYnQxO0VTw">Quan san hành - 關山行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nh%E1%BA%ADn/author-iAOn3uaLIlAHhHS3XAcQ1g">Uông Nhận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD-ph%C3%B3-An-T%C3%A2y/poem-_GtkHlhIJ7eVal-r0n0Nsw">Tặng Vi thư ký phó An Tây - 送韋書記赴安西</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%8B-Li%C3%AAu-n%C3%B4-A-%C4%90o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-S1wp55k_WtHe-BuYQH-h5w">Thị Liêu nô A Đoạn - 示獠奴阿段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
